It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: AVATAR: FIRE AND ASH TRAILER REACTION!! Avatar 3 | James Cameron
snippet.description:
NA'VI VS NA' VI?! Use code *50REELREJECTS* to get 50% OFF plus free shipping on your first Factor box at https://bit.ly/4ftNIcS!
OHHHH WE COOKIN'!! The brand‚Äënew Avatar 3: Fire and Ash trailer dropped during The Fantastic Four screenings and we lost it in the theater! Greg Alba & John Humphrey break down every jaw‚Äëdropping moment from the teaser: intense battles between Jake Sully, Neytiri and the war‚Äëlike Ash People / Mangkwan clan led by Varang (Oona Chaplin), fire‚Äëwielding Na‚Äôvi riding burning banshees, the haunting realization that the Ash People have rejected Eywa, internal Na‚Äôvi conflict and tragic grief over Neteyam‚Äôs death, Jake and Neytiri‚Äôs kids in peril‚Äîespecially young Kiri (Sigourney Weaver) facing Varang‚Äôs threat‚ÄîSpider‚Äôs shifting allegiances and Quaritch‚Äôs alliance with the Ash people‚Äîthat shot of Captain Quaritch stepping into Ash territory with red war paint was chilling. We also catch glimpses of the peaceful Wind Traders in sky‚Äëships, returning faces like Sam Worthington‚Äôs Jake Sully, Zoe Salda√±a‚Äôs Neytiri, Cliff Curtis as Tonowari, Kate Winslet as Ronal, Edie Falco‚Äôs General Ardmore, Stephen Lang‚Äôs Recombinant Quaritch, Jemaine Clement, Giovanni Ribisi, and newcomer David Thewlis as Peylak. snippet.title: How FAST Can You KILL a KILLER? [Forsaken]
snippet.description:
Forsaken is a game where survivors work together to stay alive with a killer on the loose. But when you look at the numbers, what can you discover?

In this video, I looked deeper at the Forsaken roster to break down a typical misconception about Killing Forsaken Killers. This just might help someone doing a Forsaken Challenge or even Forsaken Trolling.

And don't forget to SUBSCRIBE! We're gonna make it to 200K together!

About Forsaken:
Forsaken is a game with ten survivor characters including Noob, Two Time, Guest 1337, Shedletsky, Elliot, Dusekkar, Builderman, Chance, 007n7, and Taph. There are currently FIVE killer characters as well: Jason, C00lkidd, 1x1x1x1, John Doe, and Noli.

#roblox #forsaken #challenge

snippet.title: Destiny 2 will Die if Bungie doesn't fix this soon...
snippet.description:
Ranting about the current state of the Destiny 2 Leveling System. This is one of the Most Complained About subjects within the Destiny 2 Community after the Release of the Edge of Fate, and Bungie needs to improve this System ASAP, or Destiny 2 will be Dead. 
--FOLLOW ME ON TWITCH: www.twitch.tv/kackishd

--- My Twitter: https://twitter.com/RickKackis

New #destiny2 video, going over the current Destiny 2 Leveling System. If you want to level up fast with your gear score and reach the New Max Gear Score permanent band of 200 power, and eventually reach the new Max Gear Score (Max Level) of 450, you're in for an absolute slog! After the Edge of Fate Campaign on Legendary difficulty in the New Edge of Fate DLC, this will become extremely important! The New Edge of Fate DLC Launch is Here! We have the New Year of Prophecy and Season: Renewal (Season of Renewal) that have gone live! We have a New Edge of Fate Campaign, and Kepler, the new Edge of Fate Destination! There are many Kepler Secrets to uncover! We also have the New Sieve Activity! And we have Armor 3.0, Destiny 2 Stats Overhaul, and the New Destiny 2 Portal! All leading to the New Destiny 2: Renegades Star Wars DLC!
But today we're going over the massive problems with the Destiny 2 Leveling System! If you try to increase your Gear Score Fast, which will let you Level Up Fast with improved Score in the Portal and more Prime Engrams Drops, among other things, you have to farm the same activity for endless hours! Destiny 2 is dying and the Destiny 2 Player Count is not great, so this needs to be fixed asap!  #Destiny2News #Destiny2EdgeOfFate

snippet.title: Destiny 2 Lore - Maya asked EVERY Vex to join her. They said NO! A War of Wills!
snippet.description:
Destiny 2's Lore and Story from Edge of Fate brings us more information on Maya Sundaresh, AKA The Conductor, & her interactions with the Vex. Recently she demanded that all the Vex of the Collective at large join her faction. The Collective and a series of outliers all replied and they said no, implying that the Vex at large might soon be at War with The Conductor and her Choral Vex.
